Package com.googlecode.spring.appengine.taglib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationIdTag
    JSP Tag which outputs the application identifier for the current application.
    ApplicationVersionTag
    JSP Tag which outputs the version identifier for the current application.
    InstanceIdTag
    JSP Tag which outputs the id of the instance handling the request.
    IsAdminTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if the logged in user is an admin user.
    IsDevelopmentTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if the current executing environment is Development.
    IsLoggedInTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if there is a user logged in.
    IsNotAdminTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if the logged in user is not an admin user.
    IsNotLoggedInTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if there is no user logged in.
    IsProductionTag
    Conditional JSP Tag which evaluates its body if the current executing environment is Production.
    LoginLinkTag
    JSP Tag which renders the link that can be used to display a login page to the user.
    LoginUrlTag
    JSP Tag which returns the url that can be used to display a login page to the user.
    LogoutLinkTag
    JSP Tag which renders the link that can be used to log the current user out.
    LogoutUrlTag
    JSP Tag which returns the url that can be used to log the current user out.
    RuntimeEnvironmentTag
    JSP Tag which outputs the current executing runtime environment.
    RuntimeVersionTag
    JSP Tag which outputs the current executing runtime version.
    UserTag
    JSP Tag which allows convenient access to the logged in User object.
